to make a controller
==> php artisan make:controller {ControllerName}

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Blade Component is to use to yield or extends the view in other pages

to make class component
==> php artisan make:component {componentName}
and it creates two file
        one in App\view\component
and the other in views\component

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

change the repo

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
creating new middleware

php artisan make:middleware {middleware name}

we can use middleware global and at route

to make it global we add it in kernel.php

and individual  from the kernel.php too

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
in inner join he got all data with the relation

in left join he got all data which in the first table and the relation with it not all the records in the second table only the one with relation

in right join he got all the data in the second table and the relation with it not all the records in the first table only the one with relation

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For Creating Model
--> php artisan make:model {Model name}
